ered in scheme\n\n- [ ] Ensure shared types are properly registered\n- [ ] Update scheme builder if needed\n- [ ] Verify AddToScheme includes shared types\n\n---\n\n## Task 6: Generate DeepCopy Methods\n**Verifiable Output:** `zz_generated.deepcopy.go` contains DeepCopy methods for shared types\n\n- [ ] Run `controller-gen object:headerFile=\"hack/boilerplate.go.txt\" paths=\"./...\"`\n- [ ] Verify `DeepCopyInto`, `DeepCopy`, `DeepCopyObject` methods generated for shared types\n- [ ] Verify DeepCopy methods generated for all shared structs\n\n---\n\n## Task 7: Verify Compilation\n**Verifiable Output:** `go build` succeeds without errors\n\n- [ ] Run `go build ./pkg/apis/...`\n- [ ] Verify no compilation errors\n- [ ] Verify no type definition errors\n\n---\n\n## Task 8: Verify Import Compatibility\n**Verifiable Output:** Shared types can be imported by AR-001 and AR-002\n\n- [ ] Verify AR-001 types can import shared types\n- [ ] Verify AR-002 types can import shared types\n- [ ] Check for any circular dependency issues\n\n---\n\n## Task 9: Run Unit Tests\n**Verifiable Output:** All existing tests pass\n\n- [ ] Run `go test ./pkg/apis/...`\n- [ ] Verify no test failures\n\n---\n\n## Completion Criteria\n\n- [ ] All tasks 1-9 completed\n- [ ] Code follows project naming conventions (PascalCase structs, camelCase JSON tags)\n- [ ] Shared types are properly documented\n- [ ] Constants have descriptive comments\n- [ ] Compatible with AR-001 and AR-002 patterns\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-002/spec.yaml":[]},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-003/tasks.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-003/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775841509758,"end":1775841509778