{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775841509784,"sessionID":"ses_2879a7eb5ffe25gQOu406oxm8q","part":{"id":"prt_d7866da68001TwWXPFXkXkE99v","messageID":"msg_d786602b9001lQcENM6JIZ4DRk","sessionID":"ses_2879a7eb5ffe25gQOu406oxm8q","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_functions.write:15","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-003/notes.md","content":"# AR-003 Notes & References\n\n## Context\n\nThis change defines the shared types and constants that are reused across multiple\nCRD definitions in the AgentCube platform. These common definitions ensure consistency\nand reduce duplication across the runtime API group.\n\n## Conventions\n\n- JSON tags: camelCase (e.g., `json:\"conditionType\"`)\n- Go structs: PascalCase (e.g., `Condition`)\n- Constants: PascalCase with descriptive comments\n- API group: `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh`\n- Version: `v1alpha1`\n\n## Related Changes\n\n- AR-001: CRD AgentRuntime 类型定义 (uses shared types)\n- AR-002: CRD CodeInterpreter 类型定义 (uses shared types)\n\n## Shared Types Overview\n\n### Phase Types\nCommon phases that multiple CRDs may share:\n- Pending\n- Running\n- Succeeded\n- Failed\n- Unknown\n\n### Condition Types\nStandard condition structure following Kubernetes conventions:\n- Type\n- Status\n- Reason\n- Message\n- LastTransitionTime\n\n### Resource References\nCommon patterns for referencing Kubernetes resources:\n- Secret references\n- ConfigMap references\n- Local object references\n\n## Open Questions\n\n> Document any open questions or decisions pending.\n\n## References\n\n- [Kubernetes CRD Documentation](https://kubernetes.io/docs/concepts/extend-kubernetes/api-extension/custom-resources/)\n- [controller-runtime](https://github.com/kubernetes-sigs/controller-runtime)\n- [code-generator](https://github.com/kubernetes/code-generator)\n- [Kubernetes API Conventions](https://github.com/kubernetes/community/blob/master/contributors/devel/sig-architecture/api-conventions.md)\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-002/spec.yaml":[]},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-003/notes.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-003/notes.md","time":{"start":1775841509761,"end":1775841509780}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775841510148,"sessionID":"ses_2879a7eb5ffe25gQOu406oxm8q","part":{"id":"prt_d78660a130015vILSUXAHSi5VF","messageID":"msg_d786602b9001lQcENM6JIZ4DRk","sessionID":"ses_2879a7eb5ffe25gQOu406oxm8q","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_functions.write:10","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-003/spec.yaml","content":"id: AR-003\ntitle: CRD 共享类型与常量\nmodule: pkg/apis\nlanguage: Go\nsize: S\nstatus: open\n\n# AR-003: CRD Shared Types and Constants\n# Module: pkg/apis\n# Language: Go\n# Size: S\n\n# OpenSpec Metadata\nopenspec:\n  version: \"1.0\"\n  project: agentcube\n\n# Architecture Requirement\nrequirement:\n  type: shared-types\n  description: |\n    Define shared types and constants for CRDs in the\n    runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1 API group. This includes common\n    enums, constants, and utility types that are used across multiple CRD\n    definitions (e.g., Phase types, Condition types, common resource references).\n\n# Scope\nscope:\n  in:\n    - pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/common_types.go\n    - pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/constants.go\n    - pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/register.go updates\n  out:\n    - Specific CRD implementations (CodeInterpreter, AgentRuntime)\n    - Controller implementation\n    - Webhook validation\n\n# Acceptance Criteria\nacceptance:\n  - Shared types compile without errors\n  - Types follow Kubernetes CRD conventions\n  - Constants are properly documented with comments\n  - Common types can be imported and used by other CRD types\n  - DeepCopy methods generated\n\n# References\nreferences:\n  - https://kubernetes.io/docs/concepts/extend-kubernetes/api-extension/custom-resources/\n  - https://github.com/kubernetes-sigs/controller-runtime\n  - AR-001: CRD AgentRuntime types (precedent)\n  - AR-002: CRD CodeInterpreter types (precedent)\n\n# Estimation\nestimation:\n  size: S\n  story_points: 2\n  days: 1\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-002/spec.yaml":[],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-003/spec.yaml":[]},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-003/spec.yaml","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-003/spec.yaml","time":{"start":1775841509742,"end":1775841510145}}}}
